TEMPLATE SEARCH ORDER

The following paths are searched, in order, for template files. The first
available file is used.

Case 1: No portal configured

    1. $root/Default/templates/Default/

Case 2: Portal configured but no interface

    1. $root/$portal/templates/Default/
    2. $root/Default/templates/Default/

Case 3: Portal and interface configured

    1. $root/$portal/templates/$iface/
    2. $root/Default/templates/$iface/
    3. $root/$portal/templates/Default/
    4. $root/Default/templates/Default/

$root/Default/templates/Default should ALWAYS include a full set of templates.


TEMPLATE FILES

include/        Directory containing template fragments which may be
                included in other templates.

index.tt        Portal home page.

main.tt         Wrapper page for all templates.


STATIC RESOURCE SEARCH ORDER

    1. $root/$portal/static
    2. $root/static/

If no portal is configured, only the default will be searched.

